#originalTopic=Debate:_Abortion
It is hypocritical to protect fetuses but send men to die in war. Rick Claro - "George W. Bush will protect your unborn fetus, then send your grown child to die in war."[6] This is a common argument that undermines the notion of "the sanctity of life" and the notion that it is "inviolable". Clearly, in war, humans frequently justify killing other human beings.
